Class Books

  • java.lang.Object
    • sait.bms.problemdomain.Books
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChildrensBook, CookBook, Paperback, Periodical

    public class Books
extends java.lang.Object
    Description: Books super class that holds all common attributes for sub classes of ChildrensBook, CookBook, Paperback, and Periodical books Has 1 no args constructor and 1 with all attributes has all the getters and setters for the attributes has a toString method to print the way we want to
